            </div>

            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card animate-on-scroll">
                    <div class="feature-icon" style="background: var(--green-100); color: var(--green-700);">
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Hemat Sampai 15%</h3>
                    <p>Harga grosir yang lebih murah berkat sistem pre-order kolektif yang mengunci harga dari distributor langsung.</p>
                </div>
